01:25:57.673 --> 01:26:00.074
But Reggie, Reggie was scum.

01:26:00.942 --> 01:26:02.576
Dealer, pimp.

01:26:02.578 --> 01:26:04.111
Chelsea fan.

01:26:04.113 --> 01:26:06.947
That's three
strikes right there.

01:26:08.950 --> 01:26:11.785
