01:36:21.095 --> 01:36:23.630
- Yes, we know who you are.

01:36:23.632 --> 01:36:25.365
Thank you gentlemen.

01:36:26.600 --> 01:36:27.600
Keys.

01:36:36.410 --> 01:36:38.345
You're not a renowned author.

01:36:38.347 --> 01:36:39.980
