01:38:14.176 --> 01:38:16.342
I wouldn't hurt my mother.

01:38:16.344 --> 01:38:18.011
I wouldn't hurt her.

01:38:18.013 --> 01:38:19.013
No.

01:38:47.341 --> 01:38:48.341
- Shh.

01:47:57.824 --> 01:48:00.426
I wouldn't hurt my mother.

01:48:04.965 --> 01:48:06.599
